title: How to Get Everything Done in a Day Without Wasting Time or Getting Distracted
itunes:title: How to Get Everything Done in a Day Without Wasting Time or Getting Distracted
description: Learn practical time-management tips on becoming a homesteader and how to get everything done in a day without wasting time or getting distracted with Anne of All Trades. She shares her homesteading journey from Taiwan to Seattle, and now settled in Nashville, TN. Amidst boatloads of helpful practical advice, she shares how the phrase, "don't compare your beginning to someone else's middle" has helped her on her journey. For show notes or to read the podcast transcript, visit melissaknorris.com/290.
